  "prompt": "How do I add question details digitally on Quora?",
  "response": "To add question details digitally on Quora, follow these steps:\n\n1. **Log In to Your Account**: Access your Quora account by logging in with your credentials.\n\n2. **Ask a Question**: Click on the \u201cAsk a Question\u201d button located at the top of your Quora feed.\n\n3. **Enter Your Question**: Type your question in the text box provided. This is where you can input the main query you want to ask.\n\n4. **Add Details**: Below the question box, you may see an option to \u201cAdd Details\u201d or something similar. Click on that link or area to elaborate on your question. Here you can provide context, background information, or any specific details that will help others understand what you're asking.\n\n5. **Formatting Your Text**: You might be able to format your details using basic text formatting tools (like bold or italics) to make your question clearer.\n\n6. **Choose Relevant Topics**: You can also select relevant topics or tags associated with your question, which helps in directing it to the right audience.\n\n7. **Review and Post**: Once you're satisfied with the question and details, review your entry to check for any errors. When ready, click on the \u201cSubmit\u201d button to post your question.\n\n8. **Engage with Responses**: After your question is posted, check back for answers and engage with those who respond. You can upvote or comment on answers to facilitate further discussions.\n\nRemember that clarity and context are key in receiving the most helpful answers, so take time to phrase your question with sufficient detail.",
